graph LR
    Lidar[TFmini LiDAR range sensor] -->|Serial Distance cm| LidarProc[LiDAR range processor]
    Camera[IMX219 camera feed] -->|Frame Arrays| ONNX[YOLOv11 ONNX inference]
    
    LidarProc -->|Distance metres| Kalman[Kalman range filter]
    ONNX -->|Visual bounding box| CamDet[Camera detector parses]
    
    Kalman -->|Filtered range| Fusion[Sensor Fusion Node]
    CamDet -->|Obstacle class & azimuth| Fusion
    
    Fusion -->|Fused threat analysis| Avoidance[Obstacle avoidance logic]
    Avoidance -->|Corrective trajectory yaw| Guidance[Flight controller commands]
